---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary via-white to-tan/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl text-primary mb-4">
          About Daley Plumbing
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700">
          10 years in the pipes — and counting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Daley Plumbing started with a simple idea: that a plumbing company could be honest, skilled, and actually a pleasure to work with. Founded by a licensed plumber with over a decade in the trade, we've built the kind of business we'd want to hire ourselves.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            We're not a chain. Not a franchise. Not a side hustle. Just a local plumbing company that takes the work seriously — and treats your home like it has our name on it. Because it does.
          </p>
          <a href="/about" class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Read our full story &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-4 border-primary shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary mb-2">Straight Talk</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              No mystery charges. No runaround. We tell you what we see, what it costs, and how long it takes. That's it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-4 border-green shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary mb-2">Local Roots</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              Tacoma-built. South Sound proud. We know the neighborhoods, the housing stock, and the plumbing that comes with it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-4 border-accent shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary mb-2">Work We Stand Behind</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              Fully licensed, fully insured, and fully committed to doing the job right. Daley does it right.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-display text-primary mb-2">10+</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 font-medium">Years of Experience</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-display text-primary mb-2">Licensed</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 font-medium">& Fully Insured</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-display text-primary mb-2">13</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 font-medium">Cities Served</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
